title: Re-Up Talks w/ Steffond Johnson
desc: (Put in your own words in 1 to 2 sentances why you want to bring people together to talk about their goals and why you want to support Voltaire X to build the Re-Up app) Re-Up Talks will spotlight one person (Steffond Johnson) every day in Decemeber who will host his close family and friends to eat and talk about New Years Resolutions and social change. Come share food, ideas, and support a GoFundMe campaign for an app that PAYS YOU to stay committed to your goals. ?www.Gofundme.com/Re-Up
